From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tim2tox-bootstrap <bootstrap@local>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 19:00:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 13/13] _handleGlobalCallback: add UpdateFriendProfile to
 binary-listener passthrough

Extension of 0008's / 0011's passthrough set: when a peer renames itself
(`alice.setSelfInfo(nickName: ...)`), `V2TIMManagerImpl::HandleFriendName`
on the receiver fires `OnFriendInfoChanged` which `BuildGlobalCallbackJson`
ships as `GlobalCallbackType::UpdateFriendProfile` with the *receiver*'s
non-zero `instance_id`. Without passthrough, the Dart side early-returns
at `instance_id != 0 && !shouldPassthrough` and bob's binary-path
`V2TimFriendshipListener.onFriendInfoChanged` never fires.

Symptom: `scenario_events_virtual_test.dart`'s "Friendship listener
events" subtest times out at 15s waiting for any friendship callback
to arrive after alice changes her nickname.

The pair of follow-ups making this fix work:

  1. tim2tox C++ `ffi/dart_compat_listeners.cpp` — emit both
     `friend_profile_identifier` AND `friend_profile_update_identifier`
     fields in `FriendInfoVectorToJsonForCallback` so the Dart
     `_handleGlobalCallback` case `UpdateFriendProfile` (line 917) can
     read the userID. (Lives in tim2tox source, not in this SDK patch.)
  2. tim2tox `dart/lib/sdk/tim2tox_sdk_platform.dart` — fan
     `_notifyFriendshipListeners` / `_notifyConversationListeners` out
     to the SDK singleton list (mirror of `_notifyAdvancedMsgListeners`)
     and subscribe to `ffiService.nicknameUpdated` to push remote name
     changes through the friendship listener pipe. (Lives in tim2tox
     dart, not in this SDK patch.)

Double-dispatch risk: `UpdateFriendProfile` is dispatched per
`instance_id` payload; in toxee instance_id is always 0 so passthrough
is a no-op for the production client. The singleton listener fans out
once per non-zero instance — same shape as 0008/0011 carve-outs.
---
 .../bindings/native_library_manager.dart      | 3 ++-
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart b/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart
--- a/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart
+++ b/lib/native_im/bindings/native_library_manager.dart
@@ -403,7 +403,8 @@
           callbackType == GlobalCallbackType.UserStatusChanged.value ||
           callbackType == GlobalCallbackType.SelfInfoUpdated.value ||
           callbackType == GlobalCallbackType.UserInfoChanged.value ||
-          callbackType == GlobalCallbackType.ReceiveNewMessage.value ||
+          callbackType == GlobalCallbackType.ReceiveNewMessage.value ||
+          callbackType == GlobalCallbackType.UpdateFriendProfile.value ||
           passthroughCallbacks.contains(callbackType);
       if (instanceId != 0 && !shouldPassthrough) {
         return;
